                            </div>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-3 col-sm-2 col-lg-1"><img class="check img-fluid" src="/img/cross.png" alt=""></div>
                                <div class="col-9 col-sm-10 col-lg-11 align-middle""><p>High cost and high environmental impact</p> </div>                        
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-3 mb-2 text-center">
                            <img class="img-fluid" src="/img/hydroelectric_index.png">
                        </div> 
                    </div>
                    <p><strong>INASOLAR</strong> is presented as a <strong>pioneering</strong> R&D&I project, which aims to develop the necessary infrastructure to achieve <strong>self-sufficiency</strong> in the municipality of Aras de los Olmos, located in Valencia. It is intended that this system can be replicated by other municipalities seeking to be self-sufficient, with the numerous advantages that this entails.</p>
                    <img class="img-fluid" src="/img/Aras.png" alt="">
                    <p class="text-end "><a href="/en/project"><button class="link fw-bold p-4 mt-5">More about INASOLAR</button></a></p>
